+/**
+ * RuVector LLM WASM Integration
+ *
+ * Wraps @ruvector/ruvllm-wasm for browser-native LLM inference utilities.
+ * Provides HNSW routing, SONA instant adaptation, MicroLoRA fine-tuning,
